snippet.title: WATERMELON JELLY | Fresh Colorful Fruit Jelly Recipe Making in Village | Agar Agar Jelly Cooking
snippet.description: This video showcases the making of a healthy, fresh, and natural fruit jelly using a variety of colorful fruits, sugar, and agar agar. The combination of fresh fruits adds natural sweetness and a delightful texture, while agar agar helps create a perfect jelly consistency. This refreshing dessert is not only visually stunning but also a light and healthy treat, made using simple ingredients without any artificial additives. Watch the entire process as we prepare, set, and slice this beautiful jelly, bringing out the flavors of nature’s best ingredients in a traditional village-style preparation.

snippet.title: NZ Vs PAK 2nd T20i | Cricket Highlights | Pakistan Tour Of New Zealand | 18th March 2025
snippet.description:
In the 2nd T20I, New Zealand won the toss and decided to bowl first and invited Pakistan to bat first at the University Oval. Pakistan scored 135 runs for the loss of 9 wickets in their 15 overs. New Zealand chased down the target in just 13.1 overs and won the match by 5 wickets.

snippet.title: Sunita Williams : অকাল দীপাবলি গুজরাটে, সুনীতা পৃথিবীতে ফিরতেই বাজির রোশনাই | Bangla News
snippet.description:
Sunita Williams : পৃথিবীতে সুনীতা-বুচ। মাত্র আট দিনের জন্য International Space Station এ  গিয়ে আটকে পড়া। মহাকাশ থেকে শেষমেশ ন-মাস পর ঘরে ফেরা। চার নভোশ্চরকে নিয়ে ভারতীয় সময় ভোর তিনটে সাতাশে আমেরিকার ফ্লোরিডা উপকূলে SpaceX Dragon। নিরাপদেই অ্যাটল্যান্টিকে স্প্ল্যাশডাউন ক্যাপসুলের। পদে পদে বিপদ কাটিয়ে মহাকাশ থেকে শেষমেশ পৃথিবীতে সুনীতারা। সফল নাসা স্পেসএক্সের যৌথ অপারেশন। Hatch Closing-Undocking এর পর Deorbit Burn। কক্ষপথ থেকে বেরিয়ে নিরাপদেই বায়ুমণ্ডলে ড্রাগন। ধাপে ধাপে গতি  কমিয়ে চারটি প্যারাশুটের সাহায্যে মহাসমুদ্রে স্প্ল্যাশডাউন ক্যাপসুলের। কুলিং ডাউনের পর রেসকিউ টিম-হেলিক্যারিয়ার সাহায্যে উদ্ধার। সুনীতা-বুচদের ঘরে ফেরা। পৃথিবীর উদ্দেশ্যে রওনা দেওয়ার আগেই ভিডিওয় ঠাট্টার ছলে বার্তা। তাঁকে ছাড়া কোনও প্ল্যান নয়। জানিয়ে দিয়ে নিরাপদেই ফিরলেন ভারতীয় বংশোদ্ভূত মহাকাশচারী।

Sunita Williams : পৃথিবীতে সুনীতা-বুচ। মাত্র আট দিনের জন্য International Space Station এ  গিয়ে আটকে পড়া। মহাকাশ থেকে শেষমেশ ন-মাস পর ঘরে ফেরা। চার নভোশ্চরকে নিয়ে ভারতীয় সময় ভোর তিনটে সাতাশে আমেরিকার ফ্লোরিডা উপকূলে SpaceX Dragon। নিরাপদেই অ্যাটল্যান্টিকে স্প্ল্যাশডাউন ক্যাপসুলের। পদে পদে বিপদ কাটিয়ে মহাকাশ থেকে শেষমেশ পৃথিবীতে সুনীতারা। সফল নাসা স্পেসএক্সের যৌথ অপারেশন। Hatch Closing-Undocking এর পর Deorbit Burn। কক্ষপথ থেকে বেরিয়ে নিরাপদেই বায়ুমণ্ডলে ড্রাগন। ধাপে ধাপে গতি  কমিয়ে চারটি প্যারাশুটের সাহায্যে মহাসমুদ্রে স্প্ল্যাশডাউন ক্যাপসুলের। কুলিং ডাউনের পর রেসকিউ টিম-হেলিক্যারিয়ার সাহায্যে উদ্ধার। সুনীতা-বুচদের ঘরে ফেরা। পৃথিবীর উদ্দেশ্যে রওনা দেওয়ার আগেই ভিডিওয় ঠাট্টার ছলে বার্তা। তাঁকে ছাড়া কোনও প্ল্যান নয়। জানিয়ে দিয়ে নিরাপদেই ফিরলেন ভারতীয় বংশোদ্ভূত মহাকাশচারী।

snippet.title: Sunita Williams Return to Earth Process Explained | సునీతా విలియమ్స్ భూమ్మీదకు వచ్చే విధానం ఇలా| ABP
snippet.description:
#sunitawilliams #Nasa #SpaceX #Crew9 #Interantionalspacestation #ABPDesam #telugunews

   నాసా ఆస్ట్రానాట్, మన భారతీయ మూలాలున్న మహిళ సునీతా విలియమ్స్ తొమ్మిదినెలలుగా అంతరిక్షంలోనే చిక్కుకుపోయారని మనకందరికీ తెలుసు కదా. ఎట్టకేలకు ఆమె భూమ్మీదకు దిగే ప్రక్రియ ఈ మంగళవారం ప్రారంభం అవుతోంది. క్రూ10 అంతర్జాతీయ అంతరిక్ష కేంద్రానికి వేసుకొచ్చిన ఎలన్ మస్క్ స్పేస్ ఎక్స్ వాళ్ల డ్రాగన్ క్యాప్సూల్ లోనే క్రూ 9 భూమ్మీదకు దిగుతోంది. క్రూ 9లో మొత్తం నలుగురు ఉంటారు. సునీతా విలియమ్స్ తో పాటు స్పేస్ లో చిక్కుకుపోయిన బుచ్ విల్ మోర్...ఇంకా నిక్ హేగ్, రష్యా కాస్మోనాట్ అలెగ్జాండర్ గోర్బునోవ్ కూడా ఉంటారు. అయితే వీళ్లు భూమ్మీదకు దిగే ప్రోసెస్ దశల వారీగా జరుగుతుంది. అవేంటో డీటైల్డ్ గా చెప్పుకుందాం.


Sunita Williams Return to Earth Process Explained | సునీతా విలియమ్స్ భూమ్మీదకు వచ్చే విధానం ఇలా| ABP

snippet.title: NZ Vs PAK 1st T20i | Cricket Highlights | Pakistan Tour Of New Zealand | 16th March 2025
snippet.description:
In the 1st T20I, New Zealand won the toss and decided to bowl first and invited Pakistan to bat first. Pakistan was cheaply dismissed on the score of 91 runs in 18.4 overs. New Zealand chased down the target in just 10.1 overs and won the match by 9 wickets. 
.
.

en.description:
#AurangzebTomb #AurangzebControversy #AurangzebNews
Aurangzeb Tomb Controversy news : महाराष्ट्र में औरंगज़ेब की कब्र को हटाने की मांग हिन्दू संगठनों की तरफ से जोरो में की जा रही है. VHP और बजरंग दल ने सरकार को अल्टीमेटम दिया है. इसी बीच हमारी टीम छत्रपति संभाजी नगर पहुंची और यहां पहुंचकर हमने औरंगज़ेब की कब्र के आस पास के दुकान वालो से बात की और उनसे जानने की कोशिश की की आखिर वो क्या सोचते है औरंगज़ेब की कब्र पर चल रही इस राजनीती को लेकर.

Aas Paas Episode 17 - [Eng Sub] - Laiba Khan - Ali Ansari - 18th March 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Aas Paas is a story of love, sacrifice, and the struggles within the relationships we often take for granted.
Arshia, a strong-willed young woman, is determined to reunite her broken family after her father abandons them. Meanwhile, Dr. Saham, a dedicated professional carrying his own burdens,
crosses paths with her.
Bound by their selflessness, they embark on a journey where their devotion to family is tested, and their own happiness is put on the line.
Will Arshia succeed in bringing her family back together? What challenges await Dr. Saham and Arshia? Could love blossom between them?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Muhammad Iftikhar Iffi
Writer: Samra Bukhari

snippet.title: NASA’s SpaceX Crew-9 Undocking
snippet.description:
Watch as the four members of NASA's SpaceX Crew-9 mission—NASA astronauts Nick Hague, Suni Williams, Butch Wilmore, and cosmonaut Aleksandr Gorbunov—undock from the International Space Station and begin their journey home to Earth.

Crew-9's SpaceX Dragon spacecraft is scheduled to undock from the International Space Station at 1:05 a.m. EST (0505 UTC). After undocking from the station, Crew-9 is scheduled to splash down off the coast of Florida at 5:57 p.m. EDT (2157 UTC), ending their multi-month mission in low Earth orbit.

See the full schedule for Crew-9's return to Earth: https://go.nasa.gov/4iWeg8N
Learn more about Crew-9's scientific mission: https://go.nasa.gov/4bWdt5u
Follow the latest Crew-9 mission updates: https://www.nasa.gov/blogs/commercialcrew/

Credit: NASA

Crew-9's SpaceX Dragon spacecraft is scheduled to undock from the International Space Station at 1:05 a.m. EST (0505 UTC). After undocking from the station, Crew-9 is scheduled to splash down off the coast of Florida at 5:57 p.m. EDT (2157 UTC), ending their multi-month mission in low Earth orbit.

See the full schedule for Crew-9's return to Earth: https://go.nasa.gov/4iWeg8N
Learn more about Crew-9's scientific mission: https://go.nasa.gov/4bWdt5u
Follow the latest Crew-9 mission updates: https://www.nasa.gov/blogs/commercialcrew/

Credit: NASA

snippet.title: ‌UP Mosque Covered in Tarpuline : হোলি উৎসবে যোগীরাজ্যে মসজিদ ঢাকল ত্রিপলে এ কোন ভারত! N18P
snippet.description:
‌UP Mosque Covered in Tarpuline : মার্চেই শুরু হয়েছে পবিত্র রমজান মাস। একে রমজান তায় আবার শুক্রবার। সেদিনই আবার দোলপূর্ণিমা। কীভাবে সামাল দেবে? 
চিন্তায় ছিল ‌যোগী সরকার। তবে সমাধান মিলেছে। ইতিমধ্যেই প্রয়াগরাজে ১৪ তারিখ। রমজানের নামাজ পরার সময়ে। দুপুর ২টোর পর পিছিয়ে নিয়ে ‌যাওয়া হয়েছে। এছাড়াও দোলের রঙের থেকে বাঁচাতে।  উত্তরপ্রদেশের ৪টি জেলার প্রায় ১৮৯ টি মসজিদকে ঢাকা হয়েছে ত্রিপলে ।

snippet.title: Sunita Williams Countdown to Earth 🔥 🚀 | Madan Gowri | Tamil | MG Squad 🖖🏻
snippet.description:
In this video, Madan Gowri explains the highly anticipated return of astronaut Sunita Williams after spending months in space aboard the International Space Station (ISS). After her 9-month mission, she is set to return to Earth safely soon, facing a re-entry through Earth’s atmosphere. This process exposes astronauts to extreme G-forces, pushing their bodies to the limit. After months in microgravity, astronauts experience muscle loss, weakened bones, and balance issues, making the transition back to Earth’s gravity a major challenge. The final stage of her return? A high-speed descent and a dramatic splashdown in the ocean. Even after landing, she’ll need time to recover from space travel. But how does NASA prepare astronauts for this? What changes will she face during re-entry and splashdown? Will it be a smooth landing or a bumpy ride back home? This return will test her mental and physical endurance like never before.  With space exploration expanding towards the Moon, Mars, and beyond, missions like these are crucial for the future of human spaceflight. Could India play a role in future interplanetary missions? Stay tuned to find out!

snippet.title: Phone Ma Status Gum Na Rakhe | Reshma Thakor, Dinesh Thakor | New Gujarati Sad Song 2025
snippet.description:
સાંભળો રેશમા ઠાકોર અને દિનેશ ઠાકોર નું નવું હૃદયસ્પર્શી ઈમોશનલ ગીત "ફોન મા સ્ટેટસ ગમ ના રાખે" માત્ર @SaregamaGujarati  પર.

Credits:
Title : Phone Ma Status Gum Na Rakhe
Singer : Reshma Thakor, Dinesh Thakor
Producer: Red Velvet Cinema
Artist : Dinesh Thakor, Vidhi Shah, Bharat Chaudhary
Director, Concept & Edit : Rakesh Kumar (RK Sir)
Music: Shashi Kapdiya
Lyrics: R.K.Thakor
Creative Producer: Dhyey Films & Team
Technical Support: Jenish Talaviya
D.O.P :  Prakash Patel
Drone : Veersinh
Co Artist : Hasmukh Thakor, Arvind Manekpura, Smita, Jakir Pathan
Makeup & Hair : Smita Goswami
Production : Veersinh
SP. Thanks : Kamlesh Raval, D.A. Vaghela, Sadulkhan Pathan
Light : Kalpesh Jadav
Poster Design : Pradip Karbatiya

Lyrics:
હે અલ્યા એ ફોન મો સ્ટેટસ ગમના રાખે
રાખે દર્દીલા ગીત તારે શું દુઃખ પડ્યુ લ્યા
હે અલી એ વાત કેતા મારી જીભ ના ઉપડે
ઉપડે ના મારો પગ  ખોટી તારી વાત મળી સે
હો વાત કરી હોય એ મોણસને લાવો મારી હોમે
ઘરની માતા એ દીવા ઉપડાવું હેડો મારા ગોમે
હે અલી એ તુ કેતો હું પ્રૂફ બતાવુ
બતાવું ફોટા ફોનમાં તેતો સેલ્ફી પાડ્યા
હો મેતો ગોડા ગોમ સોડ્યું તારા વિશ્વાસે
તને નઇ ભુલું મારા છેલ્લા આ શ્વાસે
હો હૂતો બેઠો હતો ખાલી તારા રે ભરોસે
ઘરે શું જવાબ આલુ મારે હવે મરો સે
હો ઘરનો તારો ઉંબરો કદી હુનો નઇ પડવાદુ
તૂ કેતો હું ગોમનિ બારે જવાનું રેવાદુ
હે અલી હે રોજ ઓટા તુ ગોમમાં મારે
મારે તુ મેઠા ટોન ખોટું મને ગમતું નથી
હો  જીવું સુ તને જોઈને જિવવાદે
હગી ઓખે ભલે જોયુ પડતુ એ રેવાદે
હો તારાથી કંટાળ્યો હવે મને તુ મરવાદે
ગોમમા લાગે બધા વસે નઇ જીવવાદે
હો હગઇ કરી એ મુરતિયો ફરવા મને લઈ જ્યો
ફોટા ફર્યા વોટસઅપ માં પસ્તાવો મને થઈ જ્યો
હે અલી એ તારે મારે હવે મેળ નઇ પડે
નઇ પડે હવે રાત મોઢું તારું ભાળવુ નથી

pa.title: ਕੀ ਤੁਸੀਂ ਇੱਕ ਸਵੈ-ਚਲਾਉਣ ਵਾਲੀ ਕਾਰ ਨੂੰ ਠੱਗ ਸਕਦੇ ਹੋ?
pa.description:
ਲੇਜ਼ਰਾਂ ਦੀ ਤਾਕਤ ਨੂੰ ਕਦੇ ਘਟਾ ਨਾ ਅੰਕਣਾ! ਇਕ ਇੰਜੀਨੀਅਰ ਵਾਂਗ ਸੋਚਣਾ ਸਿੱਖਣ ਵਿੱਚ ਮਜ਼ਾ ਆਉ ਜਾਂਦਾ ਹੈ ਅਤੇ http://crunchlabs.com/Lidar 'ਤੇ 2 ਮੁਫਤ ਬਾਕਸ ਪ੍ਰਾਪਤ ਕਰੋ।

ਆਪਣਾ ਕ੍ਰੰਚ ਲੈਬਸ ਬਾਕਸ ਅੱਜ ਹੀ ਪ੍ਰਾਪਤ ਕਰੋ:
ਬੱਚਿਆਂ ਲਈ ਬਿਲਡ ਬਾਕਸ ਇੱਥੇ ਕਲਿੱਕ ਕਰੋ: http://crunchlabs.com/Lidar
ਟੀਨ ਏਜਰ ਅਤੇ ਵੱਡਿਆਂ ਲਈ ਹੈਕ ਪੈਕ ਇੱਥੇ ਕਲਿੱਕ ਕਰੋ: http://crunchlabs.com/LidarHP

ਸਾਡੇ ਨਾਲ ਆਪਣੀ ਲਾਈਡਰ ਕਾਰ ਟੈਸਟ ਕਰਨ ਲਈ ਲੂਮਿਨਾਰ ਦਾ ਧੰਨਵਾਦ: https://www.luminartech.com/

ਰਾਕ ਰੋਬੋਟਿਕ ਦੇ ਹੈਰਿਸਨ @IndianaDrones ਦਾ ਧੰਨਵਾਦ ਜੋ ਆਪਣੇ ਬਹੁਤ ਕੂਲ ਲਾਈਡਰ ਨਾਲ ਮਦਦ ਕਰਨ ਲਈ ਸਾਨੂੰ ਮਿਲੇ। ਇਸ ਪ੍ਰਜੈਕਟ ਤੋਂ ਸਕੈਨਸ ਅਤੇ ਕ੍ਰੰਚ ਲੈਬਸ ਦਾ 3D ਟੂਰ ਦੇਖਣ ਲਈ ਤੁਸੀਂ https://www.rockrobotic.com/ 'ਤੇ ਜਾ ਸਕਦੇ ਹੋ।

ਵੀਡੀਓ ਵਿੱਚ ਕੁਝ ਸੰਗੀਤ ਪ੍ਰਦਾਨ ਕਰਨ ਲਈ ਇਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਲੋਕਾਂ ਦਾ ਧੰਨਵਾਦ:
ਪੌਂਡਰ - @Pondermusic   
ਲੌਰਾ ਸ਼ਿਗਿਹਾਰਾ - @supershigi

ml.title: ഒരു സ്വയംനടക്കുന്ന കാറിനെ നിങ്ങള്‍ക്ക് തട്ടിപ്പുകളയാത്തുണ്ടോ?
ml.description:
'ഫ്രീക്കിങ്' ലേസറുകളുടെ ശക്തിയെ വിലകുറച്ചു കാണരുത്! എഞ്ചിനീയറിന്റേതുപോലെ ചിന്തിക്കാൻ അഭ്യസിക്കാൻ രസകരമാക്കുക, തെരഞ്ഞെടുക്കൽ: http://crunchlabs.com/Lidar ൽ രണ്ട് സൗജന്യ ബോക്സ് ലഭിക്കൂ.

നിങ്ങളുടെ കുഞ്ഞുങ്ങളായും യുവാക്കളായും അഡൾട്ട്സായും ക്രഞ്ച്‌ലാബ്സ് ബോക്സ് ഇന്ന് ലഭ്യമാക്കൂ:
കുട്ടികൾക്കായുള്ള ബിൽഡ് ബോക്സ് ഇവിടെ ക്ലിക്ക് ചെയ്യുക: http://crunchlabs.com/Lidar
എടുകാർക്കും എന്നപോലെ എടുക്കാനായ് ഹാക്ക് പാക്കും ഇവിടെ ക്ലിക്ക് ചെയ്യുക: http://crunchlabs.com/LidarHP

ലുമിനാറിനെ നന്ദി, അവരുടെ ലിഡാർ കാർ പരീക്ഷിക്കാൻ അനുവദിച്ചതിന്: https://www.luminartech.com/

റോക്ക് റോബോട്ടിക്യിലെ ഹാരിസൺ @IndianaDrones യുടെ വളരെ ത്രസിപ്പിക്കുന്ന ലിഡാറിനൊപ്പം സഹകരിക്കാന് നന്ദി. നിങ്ങളുടെ പ്രോജക്ടിന്റെ സ്കാൻഗലകളും ക്രഞ്ച്‌ലാബ്സിന്റെ 3ഡി ടൂറും സന്ദർശിക്കാൻ https://www.rockrobotic.com/ സന്ദർശിച്ചുകൊണ്ട്.

വിഡിയോയിലെ ചില സംഗീതങ്ങൾ നൽകുന്ന ഈ ആളുകളോടും നന്ദി:

ta.title: நீங்கள் ஒரு தானியங்கி கார் செகலை ஏமாற்ற முடியுமா?
ta.description:
விசித்திரமான லேசர்களின் சக்தியை எప్పుడும் தாழ்த்திக் கண்டுகொள்ள வேண்டாம்! ஒரு பொறியாளர் போன்று யோசிப்பதைப் பழகி மகிழுங்கள் மற்றும் 2 இலவச பெட்டிகளைப் பெறுங்கள்: http://crunchlabs.com/Lidar

உங்கள் க்ரஞ்ச் லேப்ஸ் பெட்டியை இன்று பெறுங்கள்:
குழந்தைகளுக்கான பில்ட் பாக்ஸ் இங்கு கிளிக் செய்யவும்: http://crunchlabs.com/Lidar
இளஞ்சிறார்களுக்கும் பெரியவர்களுக்கும் ஹேக் பேக் என்பது இங்கு கிளிக் செய்யவும்: http://crunchlabs.com/LidarHP

அவர்களின் லிடார் காரை சோதிக்க அனுமதித்த Luminar-க்கு நன்றி: https://www.luminartech.com/

மிகவும் களைக்கும் லிடாருடன் உதவியதற்காக ராக் ரோபாட்டிக் நிறுவனத்தின் ஹாரிசன் @IndianaDrones-க்கு நன்றி. திட்டத்தின் ஸ்கேன்கள் மற்றும் கிரஞ்ச் லேப்ஸ் 3D டூரைப் பார்க்க  நீங்கள் செல்லவேண்டிய இடம்: https://www.rockrobotic.com/

te.title: మీరు స్వయంచాలిత కార్‌ని మోసం చేయగలరా?
te.description:
ఫ్రీకిన్' లేసర్స్ శక్తిని అస్సలు తక్కువ అంచనా వేయకండి! ఇంజనీర్లలా ఆలోచించడం నేర్చుకోవడంలో సరదాగా గడపండి మరియు 2 ఉచిత బాక్స్‌లను పొందండి: http://crunchlabs.com/Lidar

మీ క్రంచ్‌లాబ్స్ బాక్స్‌ను ఈ రోజు పొందండి:
పిల్లల కోసం బిల్డ్ బాక్స్ ఇవ్వరానికి ఇక్కడ క్లిక్ చేయండి: http://crunchlabs.com/Lidar

Aas Paas Episode 15 - [Eng Sub] - Laiba Khan - Ali Ansari - 16th March 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Aas Paas is a story of love, sacrifice, and the struggles within the relationships we often take for granted.
Arshia, a strong-willed young woman, is determined to reunite her broken family after her father abandons them. Meanwhile, Dr. Saham, a dedicated professional carrying his own burdens,
crosses paths with her.
Bound by their selflessness, they embark on a journey where their devotion to family is tested, and their own happiness is put on the line.
Will Arshia succeed in bringing her family back together? What challenges await Dr. Saham and Arshia? Could love blossom between them?

Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4347 - Jethalal ne Diya Taarak Ko Surprise Gift?! | Taarak Mehta ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Tapu ki Shadi | Gokuldham Society | Sonu ki shadi

Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada

Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide

Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi

snippet.description:

Bhide has been well accounted for and held responsible by the Gada family for Champaklal's plight. His apologies are not working and the only solution left now is that Champak chacha returns home. Will this problem receive a permanent solution?Find out in this episode. 

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 10
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2025  #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta #comedyscene #tmkocbestcomedy 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch more episodes from 'Comedy Scenes' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cS8wi0cuF6h1ZN4wQuXjH2m

snippet.description:
Hey Guys 
This Video has everything that happens during Holi Festival .  

#partnership

This video is filled with Festive season memories and situations we all have been in . This Holi Video has every Holi situation we experience. How Indians celebrate holi . The crazy masti of Holi . Revenge wali holi , pyaar wali holi , dosto ke sath , holi fest ki holi , deciding holi songs playlist , grooving on ap dhillon songs , enjoying bhang thandai , beer , gol gappe , dahi bhalle , gujia sweets , getting gifts from relatives gulal , rang , all the colors , pichkari , desi ghee gujia , hugging enemies sorting out the grudges , hitting with water balloons , water guns , dancing , enjoying holika dhayan , the festival of colors , Taking out revenge by applying colours, the foodies, getting painted first by the bf/gf, mixing pakka color into herbal colors, Exams and holi , balloon horror created in society that we go through in holi days, and The Best Holi Fight between two groups.. , Well you will love it and Relate with this video.. Enjoy and laugh out loud. 
Do Share it with everyone, Comment your fav part and like krdena Video guys.. Subscribe the Channel for more amazing videos . 
This video is filled with such memories and situations we all have been in. 
Relish and Relive your Childhood Memories.. You will have major nostalgia

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah: 
https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7ZFhouqhrvP3Sx0U7qxdzJi
